</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="12.[187,1398,311,408]" pageId="12" pageNumber="129">
<taxonomicName authority="Vargas, 2021" authorityName="Vargas" authorityYear="2021" box="[189,446,311,337]" class="Insecta" family="Heliodinidae" genus="Helioandesia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="129" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tarregai" status="gen. et sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[189,446,311,337]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="129">Helioandesia tarregai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[451,621,312,338]" pageId="12" pageNumber="129" rank="species">gen. et sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
is named in memory of the eminent Spanish guitarist and composer Francisco Tárrega, for his huge contribution to the repertory of the classical guitar, especially for the wonderful ʻMarietaʼ.
</paragraph>
